label: SupplyChainEvent
comment: A significant occurrence or happening in a supply chain.

datatypeProperties.comment: Binary object data, such as a photograph, describing this supply chain event.
The date, time, date time, or other date time value of the due date specified by these trade payment terms.
The date, time, date time, or other date time value of the earliest occurrence of this supply chain event.
The code specifying a frequency for this supply chain event.
The date, time, date time, or other date time value of the latest occurrence of this supply chain event.
A date, time, date time, or other date time of an occurrence in this supply chain schedule.
A time value of an occurrence of this supply chain event.
A code specifying a type of MDH health indication.

objectProperties.comment: A reference associated with this supply chain event.
A reference to a physical location or place.
A logistics location where this supply chain event occurs.
A prominent attribute or aspect of an object, such as recyclability of a product, which can meet customer needs without compromising the ability of future generations to meet their own needs.
A prominent technical attribute or aspect.
